”。</a> “这是一件多么美好的事情啊，”他继续说道。 “她现在是一个真正的现象，看到所有这些年轻人真正参与全国性讨论真是令人兴奋。我认为这很令人兴奋，我很高兴看到她订婚。”</p><p>克鲁尼早在七月就支持哈里斯，他告诉<em><a href="https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/kamala-harris-biden-trump-election-07-23-24#h_031828f78423dccad4f2c433f5a0a654" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" data-type="link" data-id="https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/kamala-harris-biden-trump-election-07-23-24#h_031828f78423dccad4f2c433f5a0a654">美国有线电视新闻网</a></em>：“拜登总统已经展示了什么是真正的领导力。他再次拯救了民主。我们都很高兴能够尽我们所能来支持哈里斯副总统的历史性追求。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elizabeth-olsen-remembers-being-starstruck-meeting-george-clooney-3796710">伊丽莎白·奥尔森 (Elizabeth Olsen) 回忆起与乔治·克鲁尼 (George Clooney) 会面时的“追星经历”</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
由于对捕鲸活动的担忧，大逃亡组织取消了法罗群岛的国家合作伙伴地位https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-great-escape-withdraws-faroe-islands-country-partner-over-concerns-whaling-practices-3796731?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-great-因担忧捕鲸活动而退出法罗群岛国家伙伴Adam EnglandTue, 24 Sep 2024 20:13:04 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPolitics https://www.nme.com/?p=3796731 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大逃亡节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们认为法罗群岛艺术家的贡献不应被此事所掩盖，这与他们的艺术作品或重大成就无关”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-great-escape-withdraws-faroe-islands-country-partner-over-concerns-whaling-practices-3796731">《大逃亡》因担心捕鲸活动而取消法罗群岛作为国家合作伙伴的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大逃亡节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/The-Great-Escape-Festival-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于担心法罗群岛的捕鲸行为，在当地利益集团的强烈抗议下， <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/the-great-escape">“大逃亡”组织</a>已取消法罗群岛作为其主要国家合作伙伴的地位。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/over-100-acts-have-now-dropped-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-in-gaza-boycott-with-support-from-massive-attack-3756090">阅读更多：在 Massive Attack 的支持下，已有 100 多个艺人退出了 2024 年加沙大逃亡抵制活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>该节日每年 5 月在布莱顿和霍夫举行，当地团体对法罗群岛（丹麦王国的一部分）的捕鲸活动提出担忧后，于今晚（9 月 24 日）在 Instagram 上发布声明宣布了这一消息。该节日本月早些时候宣布法罗群岛为其主要国家合作伙伴。</p><p>在声明中，音乐节表示，多年来与法罗群岛艺术家合作感到“自豪”，并补充道，“法罗群岛音乐家一直是我们音乐节中鼓舞人心且不可或缺的一部分，我们将继续致力于支持这些令人难以置信的艺术家，因为他们继续吸引全世界观众。”</p><p>它接着说，包括苏塞克斯海豚项目在内的当地利益团体对法罗群岛的捕鲸活动提出了担忧，并澄清这些问题与那里“蓬勃发展的音乐场景”无关。声明继续说道：“我们认为法罗群岛艺术家的贡献不应因此事而黯然失色，这与他们的艺术作品或重大成就无关。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAT0pIFtl6M/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="displa